desc: The QueenBee is an all-natural, organic, immune support shot infused with honeybee byproducts. The ingredients are royal jelly, raw honey, propolis, Ginkgo Biloba leaf extract, ginger, cayenne pepper, and turmeric. All our ingredients are sourced sustainably and fresh from honeybee hives and high-quality vendors.

layout.text: Immune support line infused with honeybee by-products.
